## Features

{% include 'partials/features.md.jinja' %}

### Feature Groups

Enable curated language sets instead of individual languages:

```toml
[dependencies]
ts-pack-core = { version = "{{ project.version }}", default-features = false, features = ["web"] }
```

Available groups: `all` (default), `web`, `systems`, `scripting`, `data`, `jvm`, `functional`.

